kenapa begitu baik hati?

63
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,680
Alasannya sangat sederhana.

64
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:36,800
Aku mau tusuk konde Phoenix,
beserta nyawa Cang Hanyu dan Nan Si.

65
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:44,120
